tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE,
    partnership_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
	partnership_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	partner_name TEXT NOT NULL,
	contact_person TEXT,
	collaboration_type TEXT,
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_activities (
	activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	partnership_id UUID REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id),
	activity_name TEXT NOT NULL,
	activity_date DATE,
	org_involved TEXT,
	activity_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE resources (
	resource_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	resource_name TEXT NOT NULL,
	quantity INT,
	cost DECIMAL,
	partner_id UUID REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
	id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	organization_name VARCHAR(255),
	partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE,
	description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
	id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	partnership_id UUID,
	contact_name VARCHAR(255),
	email VARCHAR(255),
	phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_activities (
	id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	partnership_id UUID,
	activity_name VARCHAR(255),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE,
	description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE resources (
	id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	partnership_id UUID,
	resource_name VARCHAR(255),
	resource_type VARCHAR(50),
	quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_information (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    organization_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_person VARCHAR(255),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_resources (
    resource_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    resource_name VARCHAR(255),
    resource_type VARCHAR(100),
    quantity INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnership_information(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_activities (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    activity_name VARCHAR(255),
    activity_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnership_information(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_contacts (
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    contact_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255),
    contact_number VARCHAR(20),
    role VARCHAR(100),
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnership_information(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    reviewer_name VARCHAR(255),
    review_date DATE,
    rating INT,
    review_comments TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnership_information(partnership_id)
);
